  <id>nvvp.desktop</id>
  <name>NVIDIA Visual Profiler</name>
  <summary>Performance profiling tool for CUDA C/C++ applications.</summary>
  <description>
  <p>
   The NVIDIA Visual Profiler is a cross-platform performance profiling tool
   that delivers developers vital feedback for optimizing CUDA C/C++
   applications. 
  </p>
  <ul>
   <li>Focus on the information that matters</li>
   <li>Automated performance analysis</li>
   <li>Unified CPU and GPU Timeline</li>
   <li>CUDA API trace</li>
   <li>Drill down to raw data</li>
   <li>Compare results across multiple sessions</li>
   <li>Analyze data collected from remote systems</li>
   <li>CUDA Dynamic Parallelism</li>
   <li>Guided Application Analysis</li>
   <li>Power, thermal, and clock profiling</li>
  </p>
</description>
